%N A394245 a(n) = a(n-1) + a(n-3) + a(n-4), a(0) = 1, a(1) = 10, a(2) = 100, a(3) = 110.
%H A394245 Tomás Guardia, Douglas Jiménez, and Alexander McCurdy, <a href="https://doi.org/10.2478/rmm-2024-0002">Fiboquadratic numbers and Rithmomachia</a>, Recreational Mathematics Magazine, Vol. 11, No. 18 (2024), pp. 17-29.
