%F A394245 a(n) = (10*F(n/2) + F((n/2)-1))^2 if n is even and (10*F((n-1)/2) + F(((n-1)/2)-1))*(10*F(((n-1)/2)+1) + F((n-1)/2)) if n is odd where F(n) = Fibonacci(n).
